 `try_main` function (see `crates\\rust-analyzer\\src\\bin\\main.rs`)\n+```rust\n+    let mut d = 4;\n+    while d == 4 { // set a breakpoint here and change the value\n+        d = 4;\n+    }\n+```\n+\n ## Demo\n \n - [Debugging TypeScript VScode extension](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=T-hvpK6s4wM)."}]}